name: JaysonCheng/Secondhand
description: A web application that provides a platform for users to sell or purchase used or unwanted items, so called secondhand items. The purpose of this web app is to promote the reuse of items to reduce the excessive usable items disposal. This web app is written in Node.js and Express.js for the backend framework, and utilized Bootstrap for the front end framework. It is also backed up with MongoDB as the database tool to store the item posts and users login information. It has a lot of other features too, check out the website url to explore about this app!
